{"title":"蝶韵","authors":["黄志凡"],"dates":[{"year":1994,"month":8,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"蝶韵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄志凡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以翩跹欲飞的姿势"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"匍伏于大地的胸膛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倾听城市奔跑的呼吸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明亮如镜的路面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打了一个漂亮的结"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是一只金灿灿的蝴蝶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便成为城市里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一首凝固的诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一处崭新绚丽的风景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢筋混凝土与心血热汗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被阳光均匀地镀亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵州桥的石板"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泸定桥的铁索"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都已楔入坚固的桥基"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而使城市的血脉格外畅流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝滞的脚步变得轻盈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巨大的双翅上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车辆蜜蜂般地盘旋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"货物、人流、信息、活力"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高速地向城市的每个角落辐射"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，蝶的韵致"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把空间和时间紧缩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把开放的潮汛与誓语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驮向远方"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}